Key Match Events: VanVleet recorded his first double-double of the season
Green and Sengun combined for 37 points
VanVleet finished 10 of 11 from the floor, including 9 for 9 from inside the arc
Spurs were undone by their 20 turnovers, which Houston converted into 20 points
VanVleet had nine points, three rebounds and two assists in the first quarter
Landale provided nine points in the half
Green drilled a 3-pointer with 28.1 seconds left in the third, leading 94-68
Houston extended that advantage to 29 points in the final period
